"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"中共驚制裁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死幾千萬人都唔驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"自己被制裁wor"},{"pid":"8d202b1d3fe1445e17800a5d92a2709a65d1ada9","tid":1772386,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfYWoG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfYWoG3.jpg&h=092c51a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5Pnjfp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5Pnjfp.jpg&h=463d1916&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRgdqVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRgdqVq.jpg&h=0b552dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WV2jfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WV2jfr.jpg&h=804ec94e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫埋身邊7個同事/朋友就可以成立1個工會,成為勞工界登記選民(呢個界別選民=工會)。<br />\n如有5000人做左, 都已經多5000/7=700幾個登記選民, 可以直接將手足送入勞工界功能組別於立法會(輕鬆3席全取)&amp;特首選委(60席)<br />\n<br />\n嗰D會話「要真普選啊，爭咩功能組別啊？」其實任何有得做嘅野都要做。何況呢個係無咩cost而可以有效地作出影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5-%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E8%BC%B8%E4%BA%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2588%25A5-%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%259D%259C%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E4%25BA%2586%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruST1kznsNOvA2%